{
  "stem": "21626.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "But he decided they weren't going to touch the lavatory so that we could alter that saying together when I'd came back.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And anyway, I rang the bell of our flat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And of course, a strange woman answered.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And I went inside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "She just beckoned me in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "She-- I didn't have to say anything to her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And I first went on the veranda, enclosed veranda, where my father used to have his afternoon naps and I used to play with Marta.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And there was a strange young lad on-- on the floor mending his bicycle.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And the toilet in the bathroom ran off the veranda, and I impulsively opened the door to the lavatory.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And there it was still-- goodbye, my lavatory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I just cried inwardly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm here, father, but where are you?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why aren't you here?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I just ran away from there, and I ran out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I ran through the rest of the town to the banks of the river Elbe where we so often played.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I buried my face in the-- in the grass.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And for the first time since my return, I cried and I cried all those bitter tears which needed to come and were so hard to come.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And when I dried my tears and sat in-- deep in thought, and turned back towards the town, I saw a young girl coming towards me.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was running.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She had pigtails.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as she saw me, she smiled, and I recognized her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] She was my bosom friend Marta.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Somebody must have recognized her, or maybe the people where I-- you know, who lived in our house had sent the message.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But there she came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And of course, she hugged me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we cried and laughed together.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
